description: This file declares exported API functions for the Slap Service Proxy object in SLAP, providing creation, removal, initialization, and reset methods.

methods.name: SlapCreateSrvProxy
methods.description: Creates a service proxy handle with specified context parameters.

methods.name: SlapSpoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the SLAP service proxy.

methods.name: SlapSpoRemove
methods.description: Removes a SLAP service proxy instance.

methods.name: SlapSpoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls required objects for the SLAP service proxy.

methods.name: SlapSpoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the SLAP service proxy instance.

methods.name: SlapSpoReset
methods.description: Resets the SLAP service proxy to default state.
